            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I'm mapping &lt;C-z&gt; to nop temporarily.\r\n\r\n```vim\r\nif has(\"win32\") && has(\"nvim\")\r\n  nnoremap <C-z> <nop>\r\n  inoremap <C-z> <nop>\r\n  vnoremap <C-z> <nop>\r\n  snoremap <C-z> <nop>\r\n  xnoremap <C-z> <nop>\r\n  cnoremap <C-z> <nop>\r\n  onoremap <C-z> <nop>\r\nendif\r\n```",
